  "title": "Part-Time Cook",
  "description": "<p><strong>Benefits & Perks:</strong><br />• staff discount 30%<br />• Staff meals and uniform provided<br /><br /><strong>Job Summary:</strong><br />We are seeking a talented and passionate Chef de Partie (CDP) to join our dynamic kitchen team in Singapore. The ideal candidate will have a strong culinary background and the ability to work efficiently in a fast-paced environment while maintaining high standards of food quality and presentation.<br /><br /><strong>Job Description:</strong><br />• Prepare and cook high-quality dishes according to recipes and established standards<br />• Manage a specific section of the kitchen, overseeing junior staff and ensuring smooth operations<br />• Maintain cleanliness and hygiene standards in compliance with food safety regulations<br />• Collaborate with other kitchen staff to ensure timely and efficient food service<br /><br /><strong>Job Requirements:</strong><br />• Strong knowledge of food preparation techniques, culinary trends, and international cuisines<br />• Excellent communication and teamwork skills in a multicultural environment<br /><br /><br /></p>",
